{"tid":2461640,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[新疆棉] 好失望 原來許光漢都係奶共","createTime":"2021-03-25T13:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T13:25:32.000Z","uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"08c0fc3cc301c25233eed0c0b4f5106caae1f710","tid":2461640,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQFU9UaLa1Vxn3mb2GMCCc4nbjuqWPAWsDRLiJ51hoxop?filename=CVf95kB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVf95kB.jpg&h=6e15a1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【紛紛割蓆】新疆棉花話題在內地愈燒愈烈，繼H&amp;M被共青團點名批鬥後，不少曾聲明停用新疆棉的外國品牌，也被內地網民逐一點名，包括Nike、Adidas及Uniqlo等。<br />\n<br />\n不少中港台明星亦隨即宣布，終止為這些品牌代言，包括香港歌手陳奕迅、藝人陳偉霆、Angelababy等。台灣演員彭于晏、許光漢，以及楊冪、迪麗熱巴等一眾內地明星亦有發聲明割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; 以下是終止品牌合作的明星列表：&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nH&amp;M<br />\n宋茜　黃軒<br />\n<br />\nAdidas<br />\n陳奕迅　王嘉爾　Angelababy　彭于晏　張鈞甯　易烊千璽　楊冪　迪麗熱巴　鄧倫　陳立農　向佐　任敏　丁禹兮　趙露思　彭昱暢　宋妍霏<br />\n<br />\nNike<br />\n王一博　譚松韻<br />\n<br />\nUNIQLO<br />\n王源　井柏然　倪妮<br />\n<br />\nNew Balance<br />\n孟美岐　張子楓<br />\n<br />\nConverse<br />\n歐陽娜娜　張藝興　白敬亭<br />\n<br />\nCalvin Klein<br />\n張藝興　許光漢　劉雨昕<br />\n<br />\nPUMA<br />\n許光漢　楊洋　劉昊然　李現　古力娜扎　劉雯<br />\n<br />\nTommy Hilfiger<br />\n陳偉霆　李振寧　程瀟<br />\n<br />\nBurberry<br />\n周冬雨　宋威龍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1413944012282337/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fphotos%2Fa.384058221937593%2F1413944012282337%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=b921c822\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1413944012282337/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n超失望， 佢仲係台灣最近彈起， 點解要為極權站台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7358ec75704743e1b733f45426f69e2e985477a3","tid":2461640,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"ba5a584c1d3c6131df8e37b1571ab6cc78338806","tid":2461640,"uid":77959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"靠套台劇想見你爆紅，一紅就簽支那公司，都估撚到佢要奶嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢去咗支那後有咩代表作？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}